### Rulebooks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/rulebooks
### Rulebook editions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/rulebooks/editions

### Classes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/classes

### Classes + prestige + rulebook filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/classes?includePrestige=true&rulebookIds=4,6

### Domains
GET http://localhost:3000/api/domains

### Name search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/spells/search?q=fire

### Name search + rulebook filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/spells/search?q=fire&rulebookIds=4,6

### Class + level
GET http://localhost:3000/api/spells/by-class-level?classIds=1&level=3

### Spell detail
GET http://localhost:3000/api/spells/42

